		seoDescription:
			'A personal introduction to AXIOMS, a FHUGAWZ dark pop project shaped by rupture, nostalgia, immigration, recovery and the need to turn lived experience into sound.',
		keywords:
			'dark pop, dark pop project, cinematic dark pop, experimental pop, independent artist, music production, emotional songwriting, FHUGAWZ, AXIOMS, album diary, production diary, demo reconstruction',
